name: Super Starship Space Attack
overview: Find 3 power units and leave evil spaceship. Bottom of the level has an escape area. Every power unit raises your firepower. Up / down = acceleration and brake Left / right = move your spaceship Fire = shoot 9 Levels + 2 Bonus levels 3 Game modes : Child Mode (easy) (no bonus levels) Gamer Mode (normal) (all levels) I am Legend (hard) (all levels)
